  <brief_title>Goal-orientated Therapy of Perioperative Disturbance in Hemostasis in Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Goal-orientated Therapy of Perioperative Disturbance in Hemostasis With MULTIPLATE and ROTEM in Cardiac Surgery Patients Under Platelets Inhibitors</official_title>
  <sponsors>
