  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>Point-of-Care managed</arm_group_label>
    <description>This arm includes all patients in which the hemostatic therapy is guided by POC devices e.g. MULTIPLATE (a platelet function analyzer) or ROTEM (thromboelastometry)</description>
  </arm_group>
  <arm_group>
    <arm_group_label>Conventional hemostasis lab managed</arm_group_label>
    <description>This arm includes all patients in which the hemostatic therapy is guided by conventional hemostasis laboratory data e.g. INR, aPTT, fibrinogen concentration, platelet count but no POC devices e.g. MULTIPLATE (a platelet function analyzer) or ROTEM (thromboelastometry)</description>
  </arm_group>
